Package: CONSURE
Title: Estimating Spatially Continuous Survival, Migratory Connectivity and Recovery Probability
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Saskia",
           family = "Schirmer",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "saskia.schirmer@posteo.de")
Description: Estimating survival, migratory connectivity and recovery probability in continuous space from dead recovery data. The data can be simulated by the package or committed as a dataset. The package implements the continuous and combined approach described in detail in the dissertation of Saskia Schirmer.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
